IMPORTANT CONSTRAINTS:

- All data except ROI and AI brief must come from static JSON files
- Do NOT implement any data scraping, API ingestion, or live external calls
- Assume all building, state, metro, and CV data is precomputed offline
- Use placeholder/mock data for:
  - state_scores.json
  - buildings.json
  - imagery_url
- The only backend calls allowed are:
  - POST /roi/calculate
  - POST /brief/generate
- Do NOT compute ROI in the frontend
- Do NOT implement RAG in the frontend
- The frontend is purely:
  - visualization
  - interaction
  - API consumption